         <div type="transcription">
            <p>
<lb corresp="#a1"/><gap reason="lost"/><w>mitrawarme</w><w>paikānte</w>
<w>pañä<lb corresp="#a2"/>ktäñe</w><w>perneṣṣe</w><w>akālksa</w><w>ñuweṃne</w><w>saṅkatse</w><w>āyor</w><w>wsare</w><w>amplākäṃtte</w><w>pärnā-sim</w><w>mā</w><w>pralle</w><w>ste</w></p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">Mitravarman [and] ... wrote [this book] because of the</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">wish for the dignity of Buddha[hood] [and] they donated [it] to the monastery on the [day] of the new moon. [It] is not to be taken outside of the boundary [of the monastery] without permission!</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
